 [http://darcs.haskell.org/ghc/includes/Closures.h Closures.h]::
  The layout of closures.
 [http://darcs.haskell.org/ghc/includes/Liveness.h Liveness.h]::
  macros for constructing RET_DYN liveness masks
 [http://darcs.haskell.org/ghc/includes/ClosureMacros.h ClosureMacros.h]::
 [http://darcs.haskell.org/ghc/includes/ClosureTypes.h ClosureTypes.h]::
 [http://darcs.haskell.org/ghc/includes/InfoTables.h InfoTables.h]::
